@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_jmehgt(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.abs((v0 + 0.84 / v2 + 0.04)) / wp.abs(wp.sin(v2 + 0.26)))
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.sin((v0 + 0.10 / tmp + 0.84)))
    v2 = wp.exp(v2)
    tmp = (wp.exp(wp.sin(v2 + 0.86)) * v2)
    data[tid] = v0
